        <h4>统一建模语言（UML）</h4>
        <blockquote>
##            <p>The Unified Modeling Language (UML) is a general-purpose modeling language in the field of software engineering, which is designed to provide a standard way to visualize the design of a system.</p>
##            <p>The UML 2.0 major revision replaced version 1.5 in 2005, which was developed with an enlarged consortium to improve the language further to reflect new experience on usage of its features.</p>
            <p>UML 是一种对象建模和规约语言，其设计目的是对信息系统进行面向对象的分析和设计。UML 2.5 中定义了十四种图，共分为结构图（Structure Diagram）和行为图（Behavior Diagram）两大类。类图是一种结构图。</p>
